    Weight 42 Lbs
    Lubricate bearings with WD-40

Power Supply - Tripple Output
    5 volts @ 6A
    15 volts @ 1A
    -15 volts @ 1A
    Line regulation +-0.05% for 10% line change
    Ripple 2 mv rms maximumz
    Load regulation +-0.05% for 50% load change
    Weight 15 lbs

Pulse Programmer PP-101
    A-Pulse 1-30 ms 4 volt positive
    B-Pulse 1-30 ms 4 volt positive
    Delay time 10 us - 9.99 S
    Mode Internal, External Pulse, Manual
