    Frequency Accuracy: 0.005%
    CW-RF output level -13 db
    Peak output power 150 watts (nominal)
    Mixer input level: 50 mv rms (max)
    Mixer output level: 2 v rms (max)
    mixer bandwidth: 500 khz

Receiver PR 1501
    Center Frequency: 15 MHz (nominal) Tunable
